;Label de chacun des registres
NAMEREG s0,REG_A
NAMEREG s1,REG_B

NAMEREG s2,REG_TEST
NAMEREG s3,REG_STATUS
NAMEREG s4,REG_HOUR
NAMEREG s5,REG_MINUTES
